[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    164[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **VPC enforcement framed correctly for production.** "SageMaker training and inference in VPC with VPC endpoints for S3, Kinesis, CloudWatch Logs, and KMS. Required for HIPAA workloads." This is the right baseline framing.
